jyzer.items.constantpool.types
Class ConstantMethodrefInfo

java.lang.Object
  jyzer.items.constantpool.ConstantPoolInfo
      jyzer.items.constantpool.types.AbstractReference
          jyzer.items.constantpool.types.ConstantMethodrefInfo

public final class ConstantMethodrefInfo
extends AbstractReference

Contains the following information:

  • u2 class_index
    An index into the constant_pool that is a CONSTANT_Class_info that has the field or method as a member.
  • method_info mehtods[]
    Must be a valid index into the constant_pool table. The entry at that index must be a CONSTANT_NameAndType_info structure. This entry indicates the name and descriptor of the field or method.

1.0, 2005 nov. 7.
